Here you learn more about the body in German.
If you have got a pain in the arm, you say:
*Ich habe Schmerzen im Arm *Mein Arm tut weh *Mein Arm schmerzt *Ich habe Armschmerzen *Ich habe Armbeschwerden
The little children are often saying:
*Ich habe Aua im Arm ----
(The plural article is always "die".)
